what you're doing down there?

00:04:32.640 --> 00:04:34.776 position:19% line:83% align:start
I'll be making samples
of something I'd like to bring

00:04:34.909 --> 00:04:37.245 position:16% line:83% align:start
to the tea tasting party
as a small gift.

00:04:37.377 --> 00:04:38.946 position:30% line:89% align:start
How thoughtful!

00:04:39.080 --> 00:04:40.380 position:19% line:89% align:start
Your cookies are great!

00:04:40.515 --> 00:04:42.884 position:35% line:83% align:start
Thank you,
but this is something new!

00:04:43.885 --> 00:04:45.686 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
That's a lot of sugar.

00:04:50.191 --> 00:04:51.659 position:7% line:89% align:start
Those are bonkas, aren't they?

00:04:51.793 --> 00:04:53.227 position:19% line:89% align:start
And is that honey, too?

00:04:53.761 --> 00:04:55.295 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
They're all precious commodities

00:04:55.428 --> 00:04:56.831 position:27% line:89% align:start
here in Morteln.

00:04:59.033 --> 00:05:02.402 position:7% line:83% align:start
You can't get bonkas anywhere,
but the royal capital, you know.

00:05:02.537 --> 00:05:03.771 position:10% line:89% align:start
But they're not cheap either!

00:05:03.905 --> 00:05:05.573 position:27% line:83% align:start
I had to give up
all of my spending money

00:05:05.706 --> 00:05:08.676 position:19% line:83% align:start
for months in advance,
so Dad would let me have them.

00:05:09.442 --> 00:05:10.443 position:35% line:89% align:start
What is it?

00:05:10.578 --> 00:05:12.246 position:7% line:89% align:start
You'll find out when it's done!

00:05:12.379 --> 00:05:13.748 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
Ah!

00:05:17.285 --> 00:05:18.286 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah!

00:05:18.418 --> 00:05:20.922 position:21% line:83% align:start
-It smells so sweet!
-Mm-hmm.

00:05:24.892 --> 00:05:26.459 position:35% line:89% align:start
Ah! Oh my!

00:05:26.594 --> 00:05:28.229 position:30% line:83% align:start
Being in a room
with such a sweet aroma

00:05:28.361 --> 00:05:29.764 position:24% line:89% align:start
is so intoxicating!

00:05:29.897 --> 00:05:30.765 position:33% line:89% align:start
I feel faint.

00:05:30.898 --> 00:05:31.933 position:35% line:89% align:start
[chuckles]

00:05:32.066 --> 00:05:33.668 position:35% line:89% align:start
So then...

00:05:33.801 --> 00:05:36.304 position:16% line:83% align:start
it's definitely a dessert
of some kind, isn't it?

00:05:36.436 --> 00:05:39.507 position:10% line:83% align:start
Yep! You'll just have to wait
and see!

00:05:42.176 --> 00:05:43.978 position:33% line:89% align:start
There. Great!

00:05:44.579 --> 00:05:46.180 position:24% line:89% align:start
Is it finished yet?

00:05:46.314 --> 00:05:47.447 position:35% line:89% align:start
Not quite.

00:05:47.582 --> 00:05:49.817 position:27% line:83% align:start
This is actually
the trickiest part.

00:05:55.223 --> 00:05:56.924 position:44% line:89% align:start
Wow!

00:06:00.194 --> 00:06:01.562 position:41% line:89% align:start
Voila!

00:06:02.495 --> 00:06:03.731 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
Pastry looks so happy

00:06:03.865 --> 00:06:05.465 position:10% line:89% align:start
when he's focused like this.

00:06:05.933 --> 00:06:08.603 position:27% line:83% align:start
They're so golden
and translucent!

00:06:08.736 --> 00:06:10.738 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
They're called hard candies.

00:06:10.872 --> 00:06:12.340 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
How lovely!

00:06:12.472 --> 00:06:14.742 position:24% line:83% align:start
