of stained glass!

00:06:15.176 --> 00:06:17.912 position:16% line:83% align:start
Of course, all the charm
is in the finishing touches.

00:06:20.915 --> 00:06:21.549 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:06:21.682 --> 00:06:23.517 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
A kitty!

00:06:23.651 --> 00:06:25.019 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
You got it!

00:06:25.418 --> 00:06:26.386 position:38% line:89% align:start
So cute!

00:06:26.520 --> 00:06:27.822 position:35% line:89% align:start
And now...

00:06:29.523 --> 00:06:30.390 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
A dog?

00:06:30.524 --> 00:06:31.559 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
That's it!

00:06:31.826 --> 00:06:33.160 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
A bunny?

00:06:33.294 --> 00:06:34.228 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
Correct!

00:06:34.362 --> 00:06:35.663 position:35% line:89% align:start
And now...

00:06:37.131 --> 00:06:38.299 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's, um...

00:06:38.633 --> 00:06:40.368 position:24% line:89% align:start
