00:06:40.501 --> 00:06:41.535 position:38% line:89% align:start
[laughs]

00:06:41.669 --> 00:06:43.403 position:7% line:89% align:start
That's really not a bad guess.

00:06:44.138 --> 00:06:47.008 position:27% line:83% align:start
[PAS] Obviously,
she wouldn't recognize a plane.

00:06:49.210 --> 00:06:51.946 position:5% line:89% align:start
Okay, I'll try this one out now.

00:06:53.848 --> 00:06:55.249 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
Is that a flower?

00:06:55.383 --> 00:06:57.618 position:24% line:83% align:start
[PAS] That's right!
It's supposed to be a peony.

00:06:57.752 --> 00:06:59.921 position:13% line:83% align:start
The trick is to shape them
after they've cooled down

00:07:00.054 --> 00:07:01.789 position:35% line:83% align:start
