to harden a little bit.

00:07:01.923 --> 00:07:03.791 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you're not patient,
they'll still be too soft,

00:07:03.925 --> 00:07:06.060 position:33% line:83% align:start
and the candy
won't hold its shape.

00:07:06.193 --> 00:07:09.096 position:33% line:83% align:start
It's crucial
to get the timing just right.

00:07:10.598 --> 00:07:12.033 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
How peculiar!

00:07:12.600 --> 00:07:13.601 position:19% line:89% align:start
