00:07:13.734 --> 00:07:15.369 position:38% line:83% align:start
in a lot
of different situations.

00:07:15.803 --> 00:07:18.739 position:19% line:83% align:start
But I've never seen him
make that face before.

00:07:18.873 --> 00:07:21.108 position:7% line:89% align:start
He looks so gentle and playful.

00:07:21.242 --> 00:07:23.811 position:21% line:83% align:start
Yet also so confident
and in control.

00:07:24.245 --> 00:07:26.981 position:27% line:83% align:start
He's truly giving
his all to his sweets!

00:07:32.186 --> 00:07:33.054 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh!

00:07:33.187 --> 00:07:34.522 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
Licorice?

00:07:35.289 --> 00:07:36.424 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:36.557 --> 00:07:39.093 position:21% line:83% align:start
-Is something wrong?
-No, not at all!

00:07:39.427 --> 00:07:40.795 position:24% line:89% align:start
[LICORICE exhales]

00:07:40.928 --> 00:07:43.431 position:13% line:83% align:start
It feels like such a shame
to eat them, doesn't it?

00:07:43.564 --> 00:07:45.166 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
It would be a shame not to!

00:07:45.299 --> 00:07:46.534 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:07:46.667 --> 00:07:47.802 position:21% line:89% align:start
