00:07:59.547 --> 00:08:01.382 position:30% line:89% align:start
[BOTH laughing]

00:08:02.016 --> 00:08:03.417 position:41% line:83% align:start
[AGNES]
It's infuriating!

00:08:03.551 --> 00:08:05.319 position:27% line:83% align:start
Why won't Pas be
more forward with her

00:08:05.453 --> 00:08:06.921 position:13% line:89% align:start
