00:08:07.054 --> 00:08:09.056 position:5% line:83% align:start
[JOSEPHINE] Look at how far away
from her he's standing!

00:08:09.190 --> 00:08:11.692 position:27% line:83% align:start
Come on, Pastry,
at least put an arm around her!

00:08:11.826 --> 00:08:12.994 position:41% line:83% align:start
[LUMI]
