00:08:16.564 --> 00:08:18.733 position:16% line:89% align:start
Hey, cut it out already.

00:08:18.866 --> 00:08:21.202 position:16% line:83% align:start
[AGNES, JOSEPHINE] There!
That's what I mean!

00:08:21.335 --> 00:08:24.038 position:21% line:83% align:start
[AGNES] At least grab
ahold of her hand, Pastry!

00:08:24.171 --> 00:08:25.973 position:35% line:83% align:start
[JOSEPHINE]
It's getting on my nerves!

00:08:26.107 --> 00:08:27.341 position:38% line:89% align:start
Oh, man,

00:08:27.475 --> 00:08:29.343 position:16% line:83% align:start
you just know he's making
something really tasty, too.

00:08:29.477 --> 00:08:30.945 position:41% line:89% align:start
[sighs]

00:08:31.078 --> 00:08:31.812 position:35% line:89% align:start
Good grief.

00:08:32.513 --> 00:08:34.682 position:13% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE] What do you plan
to do with the bonkas?

00:08:34.815 --> 00:08:36.784 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
Hold on. Watch this!

00:08:37.318 --> 00:08:40.187 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm coating
them with the candy I made!

00:08:41.389 --> 00:08:44.525 position:35% line:83% align:start
[LICORICE]
Ah! They're beautiful, too!

00:08:45.126 --> 00:08:46.861 position:13% line:83% align:start
That was the perfect moment
to say,

00:08:46.994 --> 00:08:49.363 position:30% line:83% align:start
"Not one-tenth
as beautiful as you!"

00:08:49.497 --> 00:08:51.432 position:13% line:89% align:start
Would you like to try one?

00:08:51.565 --> 00:08:53.634 position:30% line:83% align:start
-Are you sure?
-Of course!

00:08:54.468 --> 00:08:57.004 position:13% line:83% align:start
[PAS] They say that people
originally coated apples

00:08:57.138 --> 00:08:59.240 position:19% line:83% align:start
in caramel as a method
of preserving the fruit

00:08:59.373 --> 00:09:00.841 position:19% line:89% align:start
to make it last longer.

00:09:01.475 --> 00:09:02.810 position:24% line:89% align:start
Then I'll try one.

00:09:04.111 --> 00:09:06.213 position:38% line:89% align:start
[chewing]

00:09:06.347 --> 00:09:07.748 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:09:07.882 --> 00:09:09.350 position:33% line:89% align:start
It's so good!

00:09:09.483 --> 00:09:12.319 position:7% line:83% align:start
Once you get used to the candy,
try a bite of the bonka.

00:09:13.154 --> 00:09:14.523 position:41% line:89% align:start
[bites]

00:09:14.655 --> 00:09:15.856 position:41% line:89% align:start
Yummy!

00:09:15.990 --> 00:09:17.526 position:35% line:83% align:start
The secret
to the perfect candy bonka

00:09:17.658 --> 00:09:18.793 position:24% line:89% align:start
lies in the harmony

00:09:18.926 --> 00:09:19.927 position:21% line:83% align:start
between the tartness
of the bonka

00:09:20.061 --> 00:09:21.729 position:7% line:89% align:start
and the sweetness of the candy.

00:09:21.862 --> 00:09:23.064 position:44% line:83% align:start
-Wow!
-[chuckles]

00:09:23.197 --> 00:09:24.899 position:30% line:83% align:start
Though simple,
that delicate balance

00:09:25.032 --> 00:09:27.935 position:33% line:83% align:start
is the reason
this dessert is so well liked.

00:09:28.069 --> 00:09:30.571 position:19% line:83% align:start
And it tastes delicious
in a totally different way

00:09:30.704 --> 00:09:32.807 position:27% line:83% align:start
than just eating
a bonka on its own, too.

00:09:32.940 --> 00:09:34.875 position:30% line:89% align:start
How mystifying!

00:09:35.342 --> 00:09:36.444 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
Now, then.

00:09:36.577 --> 00:09:38.045 position:19% line:89% align:start
[footsteps approaching]

00:09:38.646 --> 00:09:40.047 position:35% line:89% align:start
[ALL groan]

00:09:40.181 --> 00:09:41.115 position:41% line:89% align:start
[thud]

00:09:41.248 --> 00:09:42.083 position:47% line:89% align:start
Ah.

00:09:42.216 --> 00:09:43.417 position:35% line:83% align:start
