could pull such a thing off.

00:18:53.601 --> 00:18:54.936 position:44% line:83% align:start
[PAS]
Accordingly,

00:18:55.069 --> 00:18:56.638 position:24% line:83% align:start
since Your Ladyship
has access to a harbor,

00:18:56.771 --> 00:18:58.873 position:13% line:83% align:start
I hoped to get your support
with distribution,

00:18:59.007 --> 00:19:01.109 position:21% line:83% align:start
