a roundabout approach

00:19:01.241 --> 00:19:02.510 position:33% line:89% align:start
to get there.

00:19:02.644 --> 00:19:04.112 position:33% line:83% align:start
So that's why
you were putting on a show

00:19:04.244 --> 00:19:05.379 position:7% line:89% align:start
