00:19:05.513 --> 00:19:07.147 position:24% line:89% align:start
Very well observed.

00:19:07.280 --> 00:19:08.482 position:41% line:83% align:start
[RETES]
Heavens!

00:19:08.616 --> 00:19:10.585 position:5% line:89% align:start
