fixed on something greater

00:19:16.289 --> 00:19:17.491 position:30% line:89% align:start
in the future,

00:19:17.625 --> 00:19:19.694 position:21% line:83% align:start
but what is he seeing
that I don't?

00:19:19.827 --> 00:19:21.062 position:35% line:89% align:start
Fine then.

00:19:21.194 --> 00:19:23.031 position:7% line:83% align:start
